sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant V as Verifier
    participant CA as Credential<br/>Authority
    note over W, CA: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>W: Generate Key
    W->>W: Create Credential Request<br/>including Key PoP
    W->>W: Create Evidence (Quote)<br/>including Credential Request
    W->>V: Request<br/>Attestation Results<br/>passing Quote as Evidence
    V->>V: Check the Evidence against Reference Values
    V->>V: Compute Credential Attributes<br/>from Evidence
    V->>CA: Request Credential<br/>passing Credential Request<br/>and Credential Attributes
    CA->>CA: Create and Sign Credential<br/>from Credential Request<br/>and Credential Attributes
    CA->>V: Credential
    V->>W: Credential in <br/>Attestation Results
